          <div className="text-xs text-muted-foreground p-3 bg-muted rounded-lg">
            <p className="font-medium mb-1">Tips:</p>
            <ul className="space-y-1">
              <li>• Enable clustering for large projects (50+ files)</li>
              <li>• Use depth 1 for top-level folders, 2-3 for nested structure</li>
              <li>• Increase level distance for cleaner hierarchies</li>
              <li>• Use Left-Right for wide graphs</li>
              <li>• Hide dynamic imports to reduce complexity</li>
